data.description:
Welcome home to this fabulous 5bd/3Bth two-story family home located in the Beautiful Gillespie Gardens neighborhood. Boasting the largest floor plan in the community (2,556 sqft), this home has all the goods. From its water softener system to the tankless water heater, you'll have peace of mind knowing this 2018 built home has all the items needed to make your family feel right at home. Plenty of room for everything! Upstairs playroom/loft would make an easy 6-bedroom conversion. Large Backyard overlooking the pond- You can watch beautiful sunsets while grilling up yumminess in the backyard. 
Extra features include *Large kitchen island with stainless steel kitchen appliances; 2 Car Garage with ample parking; Master suite includes a huge bathroom with a large tub and a gigantic walk-in closet! * Schedule your showing today! ***Seller incentive available for the carpets***
